OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fgradually fading this evening. Clear
OL,7,Fspells at first, but thicker cloud
OL,8,Fmoving westwards across eastern
OL,9,Fcounties, with drizzly outbreaks
OL,10,Fpossible. Winds strengthening in the
OL,11,Fsouth and west. Chilly where skies
OL,12,Fremain clear for longest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FEarly cloud with patchy
OL,15,Fdrizzle across some central and
OL,16,Fnorthern areas, soon clearing
OL,17,Fwestwards. Otherwise, after a chilly
OL,18,Fstart, dry with warm sunny spells for
OL,19,Fmost. Windy in the south.
